  "Jeffrey Cheah is the executive chairman of Malaysian conglomerate Sunway. ",
  "Over four decades, he transformed his obscure tin-mining company into a conglomerate with interests in hotels, education, healthcare & infrastructure.",
  "His daughter, Sarena, and sons, Evan and Adrian, work in the family business.",
  "Sunway's healthcare arm has two hospitals in Kuala Lumpur and has plans to open five more across the country. ",
  "In 2020, Sunway expanded into fintech, acquiring a 51% stake in credit reporting agency Credit Bureau Malaysia."
